  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.iotivity.service.easysetup.mediator.CloudProp.getAccessTokenType()
    OCF 1.4 Resource schema for CoAPCloudConf Resource no longer supports Access Token Type property. A default value of "Bearer" can be assumed.
    org.iotivity.service.easysetup.mediator.CloudProp.getAuthCode()
    OCF 1.4 Resource schema for CoAPCloudConf Resource no longer supports Auth Code property.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.getValueBool(String)
    use OcRepresentation.getValue(String key) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.getValueInt(String)
    use OcRepresentation.getValue(String key) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.getValueString(String)
    use OcRepresentation.getValue(String key) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcPlatform.registerDeviceInfo(OcDeviceInfo)
    use setPropertyValue instead
    org.iotivity.service.easysetup.mediator.CloudProp.setCloudProp(String, String, String)
    OCF 1.4 Resource schema for CoAPCloudConf Resource no longer supports Auth Code property.
    org.iotivity.service.easysetup.mediator.CloudProp.setCloudPropWithAccessToken(String, OAUTH_TOKENTYPE, String, String)
    OCF 1.4 Resource schema for CoAPCloudConf Resource no longer supports Access Token Type property. Recommended to use overloaded method which doesn't expect tokenType input parameter instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcProvisioning.SetownershipTransferCBdata(OxmType, OcProvisioning.PinCallbackListener)
    use OcProvisioning.setOwnershipTransferCBdata(org.iotivity.base.OxmType, org.iotivity.base.OcProvisioning.PinCallbackListener) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.setValueBool(String, boolean)
    use OcRepresentation.setValue(String key, boolean value) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.setValueInt(String, int)
    use OcRepresentation.setValue(String key, int value) instead.
    org.iotivity.base.OcRepresentation.setValueString(String, String)
    use OcRepresentation.setValue(String key, String value) instead.
